00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:46,000
 The Bible says in Proverbs 20, verse 9, "The glory of young men is their strength,

546
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,000
 but the honor of old men is their gray hair."

547
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:52,000
 In other words, young people never think they're going to get old,

548
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,000
 and they focus on their strength.

