00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:10,000
 "Charm is deceitful, beauty is vain.

552
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:15,000
 But a woman who ages, whose beauty isn't what it was in her 20s,

553
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:19,000
 who continues to fear the Lord, that's the woman you want to run with."

554
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:23,000
 And so you find a young man who walks with the wisdom of the ages

555
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,000
 and yoke yourself with him.

556
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:27,000
 You find a young woman who, she might be charming and beautiful,

557
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:30,000
 the young man might be strong, but you find one who is wise,

558
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:36,000
 and you find one who fears the Lord, and you will be blessed.

559
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:38,000
 See, that's what God wants you to do.

